## A-pet-care-platform-using-UGV

#### Evironment
>os : Ubuntu 18.04 LTS<br/>
>python V : 3.6<br/>
>robot : Turtlebot3<br/>
>simulator : GAZEBO<br/>
>ros version : melodic

# Jetson + OpenCR Setup Guide

## 1. System Setup

### 1.1 Update and Install Required Packages
```bash
sudo apt-get update
sudo apt-get upgrade -y
sudo apt-get install -y chrony ntpdate build-essential curl nano

### 1.2 Add ROS Repository and Install ROS Melodic
sudo sh -c 'echo "deb http://packages.ros.org/ros/ubuntu $(lsb_release -sc) main" > /etc/apt/sources.list.d/ros-latest.list'
curl -s https://raw.githubusercontent.com/ros/rosdistro/master/ros.asc | sudo apt-key add -
sudo apt-get update -y
sudo apt-get install -y ros-melodic-ros-base
